<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The documentation is on the following URL: <a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.validate.set.html#zend.validate.set.greaterthan">http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/â€¦</a></p>

<p>It says that "The above example returns TRUE for all values which are equal to 10 or greater than 10."
The problem is that Zend_Validate_GreaterThan will never return true if the values are equal.</p>

